Women's polo model (polo-womens.glb)
====================================

This garment was supplied by the site owner (a photogrammetry scan, provided as
a ~21.2 MB / 589k-vertex glTF, replacing an earlier scan). For the studio it was
welded, decimated with the meshoptimizer simplifier to ~77k vertices, had vertex
normals recomputed, and was re-centred and height-normalised, then re-exported
as a compact binary glTF (~3.7 MB). It carries no textures and is recoloured at
runtime.

ACTION REQUIRED: confirm the original source and licence of this scan and record
it here (author, URL, and licence terms). If the scan is under a licence that
requires attribution (e.g. CC-BY) or restricts commercial use, that must be
honoured before the site goes live.
